article.description: — Isaiah Stevens had 23 points as Colorado State routed Northern Arizona 91-52 on Monday night.
article.headline: Stevens leads Colorado State past Northern Arizona 91-52
article.linkText: Stevens leads Colorado State past Northern Arizona 91-52
article.story: FORT COLLINS, Colo. -- — Isaiah Stevens had 23 points as Colorado State routed Northern Arizona 91-52 on Monday night. David Roddy had 14 points and eight rebounds for Colorado State (2-0). James Moors and Kendle Moore each had 12 points. Cameron Shelton had 18 points for the Lumberjacks (0-3). Luke Avdalovic added 12 points and Carson Towt had seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
